title: KSJV
text: KSJV (91.5 <a href="FM%20broadcasting">FM</a>) is a <a href="radio%20station">radio station</a> broadcasting a <a href="Spanish%20Variety">Spanish Variety</a> format. Licensed to <a href="Fresno%2C%20California">Fresno, California</a>, United States, the station serves the Fresno area. The station is currently owned by <a href="Radio%20Biling%C3%BCe">Radio Bilingüe</a>, Inc. The station is also broadcast on <a href="HD%20radio">HD radio</a>.
